---
title: Veggie Mince Rogan Josh Style Curry  with Peppers and Ginger Rice
description: This Veggie Mince Rogan Josh Style Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
